General.Name: Nimfamoney
General.Description: Nimfamoney wants to be the world’s first 100% decentralized cryptocurrency lending platform for token purchase on exchanges and ICOs for maximizing your personal profit. The platform allows investors to access 0% interest on loans to invest in blockchain companies or ICO's.

ICO.Description:
Nimfamoney allows users to leverage their positions in ICO investments 3X. This increases their risk and reward to ICO investments. Nimfamoney charges a 3.3% fee for this loan and a 10% fee of profits.

Use of Funds:

  • 55% Software Developemnt
  • 15% marketing
  • 15% Operational expenses
  • 5%Reserve fund
  • 5% Expenses on legal services
  • 5% Unexpected expenses
